/*
 *   Project F1 Racing Circuit
 *
 *  F1 Racing Circuit
 *
 *  Key bindings:
 *  p/P        Cycle through different Perspectives
 *  w/a/s/d    Move POV/Drive car (in POV mode)
 *  m/M        Cycle through different objects
 *  n/N        Switch between Day and Night Mode
 *  q          Toggle axes
 *  arrows     Change view angle in perspective mode
 *  0          Reset view angle
 *  ESC        Exit
 *  [          Lower light
 *  ]          Higher light
 *  l,L        Toggle light
 *  F3         Toggle light distance
 *  
 *
 * use make command to get the binaries
 * ./final to view the project
 * Yet to simulate movement in other cars too.
 * Yet to add textures to all objects.
 */
